{"id":73,"date":"2021-09-29T03:58:46","date_gmt":"2021-09-29T03:58:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/?p=73"},"modified":"2021-09-29T11:52:05","modified_gmt":"2021-09-29T11:52:05","slug":"ii-patch-am-thanh-voi-apple-alc-with-patch-hpet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/09\/29\/ii-patch-am-thanh-voi-apple-alc-with-patch-hpet\/","title":{"rendered":"II. Patch \u00e2m thanh v\u1edbi apple alc ( with patch hpet )"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_17 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Danh m\u1ee5c<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"><\/i><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/09\/29\/ii-patch-am-thanh-voi-apple-alc-with-patch-hpet\/#Patch_am_thanh\" title=\"Patch \u00e2m thanh\">Patch \u00e2m thanh<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/09\/29\/ii-patch-am-thanh-voi-apple-alc-with-patch-hpet\/#Patch_Hpet_IRQ\" title=\"Patch Hpet, IRQ :\">Patch Hpet, IRQ :<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Patch_am_thanh\"><\/span><strong>Patch \u00e2m thanh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><b>B1:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Down kext apple alc t\u1eeb ngu\u1ed3n <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/acidanthera\/applealc\/releases\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Releases \u00b7 acidanthera\/AppleALC \u00b7 GitHub<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>B2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Down hackintool t\u1eeb ngu\u1ed3n sau <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/headkaze\/Hackintool\/releases\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Releases \u00b7 headkaze\/Hackintool \u00b7 GitHub<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>B3<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: M\u1edf hackintool v\u00e0o tab Sound v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c ALC Layout ID ch\u1ecdn layout ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o config m\u1ee5c NVRAM ==&gt; boot arg ( c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 alcid=3 )<\/span><br \/>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/gjx8zKgIrbfDE0iaY5JkMcIiago9ZvPnUUivphi1fMeeJclBNWoMpRo_XiwioV__VNZFIhkE4o5IrrpvCLti-mcuEct8qcOlmhg0xhUJsfMDhCn9HALMT9pYcXHoOEZZ53PFby2A=s0\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>B4<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Snapshot config v\u00e0 restart m\u00e1y\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>L\u01afU \u00dd: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u00e0 m\u00e1y v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn mic ho\u1eb7c ko nh\u1eadn speaker th\u00ec b\u1ea1n thay t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 layout-id kh\u00e1c (th\u1eed t\u1eebng layout-id cho t\u1edbi khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 | n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea7n hackintool m\u1ee5c sound c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n g\u00ec c\u1ea3 ( nh\u01b0 \u1ea3nh\u00a0 )<\/b><br \/>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/VsBezumgDn0Kjraq1xpqjmzVLT3TaOEAPnCzIpRgMNa8E4bWhTCGZ2PeQfB_s9eiDyFNs9wbihtGbTkr-ibQ2CXACYhsVCwWoeElkPVjwqTkb7KC6nsIT6ZSq3F0iUpsDQigxiSB=s0\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>th\u00ec b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea7n patch hpet \u1edf ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e9 ( n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 patch hpet v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u1ee9 patch b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng\u00a0 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ed7i th\u01b0\u1eddng\u00a0 g\u1eb7p \u1edf gen 10 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o linux \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh codec | n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi gen 10 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem l\u1ea1i xem patch hpet c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i g\u00ec kh\u00f4ng )<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>B1: v\u00e0o terminal g\u00f5 l\u1ec7nh sau\u00a0\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>cat \/proc\/asound\/card0\/codec#0 &gt; ~\/Desktop\/codec_dump_0.txt<\/b><br \/>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/wqEGbGfcAtCuPunnfMGD36w3lXMZWtvBvjdijD7_nlohvhDgvs8mJa7WBUQ6tjDAsvBmKk8nDihwIUA9wxm_iDxJS5QW32fMmvV4ACdmQs2ebkiJs3_2FroH9y07okT8ZAMzyYYh=s0\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>B2: t\u00ecm alc id <\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/acidanthera\/AppleALC\/wiki\/Supported-codecs\"><b>t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/b><\/a><b> )<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd 2 :\u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ea1n th\u1eed fix applehda kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 AppleALC b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch c\u00e0i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tinh ch\u1ec9nh voodoohda m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Patch_Hpet_IRQ\"><\/span><b>Patch Hpet, IRQ <\/b><b>:<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ed7i n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00e1y gen 5 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi g\u1eb7p l\u1ed7i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 \u1ea3nh\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/VsBezumgDn0Kjraq1xpqjmzVLT3TaOEAPnCzIpRgMNa8E4bWhTCGZ2PeQfB_s9eiDyFNs9wbihtGbTkr-ibQ2CXACYhsVCwWoeElkPVjwqTkb7KC6nsIT6ZSq3F0iUpsDQigxiSB=s0\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>B1<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Dump dsdt (xem h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn\u1edf m\u1ee5c <a href=\"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/09\/29\/xxvi-patch-dsdt-phan-1\/\">XXVI<\/a>)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Ch\u1ecdn D (ho\u1eb7c d) v\u00e0 k\u00e9o file dsdt c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o ti\u1ebfp nh\u1ea5n enter<\/span><br \/>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/v_l7aP6THGqwuhGA1OZEONrHCIgvf5c9KVKHrnU-XK8O26PoDtAOf7Aclv-Dek-kcq51LMdK